Label: '''hind foot length’'
Text definition: The length of a hind foot
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ''hind foot'')'

Label: '''hind foot length with claw'''
Text definition: The length of a hind foot that includes a cutaneous appendage
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ''hind foot'') and (has_part some ''cutaneous appendage'')'

Label: '''hind foot length without claw'''
Text definition: The length of a hind foot that does not include a cutaneous appendage
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ''hind foot'') and (not (has_part some ''cutaneous appendage''))'

Label: '''femur length’'
Text definition: The length of a femur
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ‘femur’)'

Label: femur length to head’
Text definition: A femur where the anatomical position of the head of the femur is the tallest point
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ''femur'') and (‘part of’ some ‘head of femur’)'

Label: femur length beyond head’
Text definition: A femur where the anatomical position of the head of the femur is not the tallest point
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ''femur'') and (‘part of’ some ‘trochanter major’)'

Label: 'femur circumference'''
Text definition: The circumference of a femur
Equivalent to: '''circumference ‘and (''inheres in'' some ‘femur’)'

Label: '''tibia length’'
Text definition: The length of a tibia
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ‘tibia’)'

Label: '''tibia proximal breadth’'
Text definition: The width of the proximal region of the tibia

Label: '''tibia distal depth’'
Text definition: The depth of the distal region of the tibia

Label: '''proximal epiphysis of tibia length’'

Label: distal epiphysis of tibia size trait’
Text definition: The size of the distal epiphysis of the tibia
Equivalent to: '''size’ and (''inheres in'' some ''distal epiphysis of tibia'')'

Label: '''distal epiphysis of tibia length’'
Text definition: The length of the distal epiphysis of the tibia
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ''distal epiphysis of tibia'')'

Label: '''humerus length above the caput’'
Text definition: The length of the humerus where the caput is not the highest point

Label: '''humerus length from caput’'
Text definition: The length of a humerus where the caput is the highest point
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ‘humerus’) and (‘part of’ some ‘proximal head of humerus’)'

Label: '''humerus circumference’'
Text definition: The circumference of a humerus
Equivalent to: '''circumference’ and (''inheres in'' some ‘humerus’)'

Label: '''humerus tubercle width’'
Text definition: The width of the tubercle of the humerus

Label: '''radius length’'
Text definition: The length of a radius
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ‘radius’)'

Label: '''distal radius breadth’'

Label: '''olecranon length’'
Text definition: The length of the olecranon
Equivalent to: '''length’ and (''inheres in'' some ‘olecranon’)'

Label: '''olecranon width’'
Text definition: The width of the olecranon
Equivalent to: '''width’ and (''inheres in'' some ‘olecranon’)'

Label: '''metacarpal proximal breadth’'
Text definition: The breadth of the proximal metacarpal
